README for scripts to reproduce chromatin segmentation using ChromHMM

ChromHMM links
	- http://compbio.mit.edu/ChromHMM/
	- https://github.com/jernst98/ChromHMM
	- http://www.nature.com/nmeth/journal/v9/n3/full/nmeth.1906.html
	- https://www.nature.com/articles/nprot.2017.124

Required inputs are:
	- path to ChromHMM install
	- peak file list
	- input folder (relative to the file locations in the peak file list)
	- output folder (where the chromatin segmentation will be stored)

Scripts
	- chromHMM_01_binarize_bed.sh
	- chromHMM_02_learn.sh
